data.description: Motivated seller, bring your offers. Step into your perfect sanctuary! This 2021-built, better-than-new home comes with the added peace of a builder's warranty. With three bedrooms, two bathrooms, a convenient two-car garage, and a welcoming patio, it's designed for modern comfort and convenience.With easy access to both highway and tollway, commuting to the city is a breeze. The split bedroom layout ensures privacy, while the open floor plan provides a seamless flow throughout. Nestled in a serene setting, this home offers a quiet country feel, providing a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle.
